# AI Automation Workflows

Automates business workflows using AI and APIs, generating daily reports and alerts for managers.

## Features
- Workflow automation with n8n
- AI-generated summaries
- Alerts for exceptions (e.g., slow bookings, negative reviews)
- Integrates Slack, Google Sheets, APIs

## Tech Stack
n8n | Python | OpenAI API | REST APIs | Slack API

## Use Case
Reduces manual reporting work and ensures managers receive timely insights for decisions.
